These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 9

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-9-1::.
There 2 different types of food: cherry, grapefruit
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: rugby, cycling
1. the person who's sport is cycling is in an odd position##4
2. the person eating grapefruit and the person who's sport is cycling have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2    |
| Food    | grapefruit | cherry  |
| Sport   | cycling    | rugby |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-9-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, tea
There 2 different types of food: zucchini, radish
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person eating zucchini have the same parity positions##9
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere to the right of the person drinking tea##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |     2     |
| Beverage   | tea      | hot-chocolate       |
| Food       | radish | zucchini |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-9-3::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: rock, indie
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: badminton, rugby
1. the fan rock and the person who's sport is badminton have different parity positions##9
2. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |
| Music-Genre   | indie     | rock       |
| Sport         | badminton | rugby |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-9-4::.
There are 2 different nationalities: brazilian, chinese
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: rugby, surfing
1. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rugby##3
2. the chinese and the person who's sport is surfing have different parity positions##9
3. the brazilian is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |
| Nationality   | chinese | brazilian |
| Sport         | rugby | surfing  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-9-5::.
