 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-9-6::.
There 2 different types of food: nectarine, tomato
2 different pets are kept: turtle, frog
1. the owner of the turtle and the person eating tomato have the same parity positions##9
2. the person eating tomato is on the left of the person eating nectarine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |   2    |
| Food   | tomato | nectarine  |
| Pet    | turtle       | frog |

